<h2><a name="gcount" id="gcount">gcount</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Syntax:
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">    streamsize istream<span class="sy0">::</span><span class="me2">gcount</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span>;</pre>
<p>

The function gcount() is used with input streams, and returns the number of
characters read by the last unformatted input operation.
</p>

<p>
Related Topics: <a href="get" class="wikilink1" title="io:get">get</a>, <a href="getline" class="wikilink1" title="io:getline">getline</a>, <a href="read" class="wikilink1" title="io:read">read</a>
</p>

